A1  -  NCT06658769,
T1  -  Use of Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation in the Post-Operative Cognitive Dysfunction in Elderly
JA  -  https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT06658769
PY  -  2024
