T1  -  Designing a randomized, sham-controlled, parallel-design trial to investigate the effects of a combined exercise priming and transcranial direct current stimulation intervention in mild cognitive impairment and alzheimer's disease
JA  -  Brain stimulation
PY  -  2019
VL  -  12
